name: PushbackIterator_pushbackIteratorTest
description: Unit tests for the PushbackIterator class in Apache Commons Collections, focusing on the pushbackIterator method.

test_cases.name: testPushbackIteratorWithPushbackIterator
test_cases.description: Tests the pushbackIterator method when provided with another PushbackIterator instance.

test_cases.name: testPushbackIteratorWithRegularIterator
test_cases.description: Tests the pushbackIterator method when provided with a regular Iterator instance.

test_cases.name: testPushbackIteratorWithNullIterator

test_cases.name: testPushbackIteratorWithEmptyIterator
test_cases.description: Tests the pushbackIterator method when provided with an empty Iterator instance.
